WEBVTT

00:02.302 --> 00:03.403
Narrator:
Tonight on "Shark Tank"...

00:03.403 --> 00:05.438
So, I rigged up a camera
inside this helmet

00:05.438 --> 00:07.407
so you can see
exactly how it looks.

00:07.407 --> 00:09.009
Now, these are cool.

00:09.009 --> 00:11.678
If you could use one word
that describes us,

00:11.678 --> 00:13.046
it's literally "clutch."

00:13.046 --> 00:14.748
So you've got to be making
a boatload of money.

00:14.748 --> 00:16.816
-Yeah.
-We're not defined by, like,

00:16.816 --> 00:19.085
our biggest successes and
the greatest of the greats.

00:19.085 --> 00:22.088
We're defined by what we do
when things get tough.

00:22.088 --> 00:23.523
You guys, I will not stop

00:23.523 --> 00:26.059
until I make this
an international company.

00:26.059 --> 00:28.628
You'll never succeed
without me.

00:28.628 --> 00:29.996
[ Sobbing ]

00:36.469 --> 00:39.539
♪♪

00:39.539 --> 00:41.574
Narrator: First in the Tank
is an accessory

00:41.574 --> 00:43.843
that is functional
and versatile.

00:43.843 --> 00:50.250
♪♪

00:50.250 --> 00:52.685
Hello, Sharks.
I'm Jenny Hutt.

00:52.685 --> 00:55.889
This is my sister Stacy.
And this is our partner Andrea.

00:55.889 --> 00:59.159
We are the team that
invented Bunny Eyez!

00:59.159 --> 01:01.528
Today we're seeking
a $200,000 investment

01:01.528 --> 01:03.930
for 10% equity
in our company.

01:03.930 --> 01:05.999
Sharks, years ago,

01:05.999 --> 01:08.768
I was sitting at the salon
having my hair colored,

01:08.768 --> 01:12.305
and I experienced a problem
that many people face.

01:12.305 --> 01:15.308
I couldn't wear my glasses and
read while having my hair done.

01:15.308 --> 01:17.477
I kept having to take
my glasses off

01:17.477 --> 01:19.913
and put them on
and take them off...

01:19.913 --> 01:22.348
just so my stylist
could do my hair.

01:22.348 --> 01:24.117
In that moment,
I said to myself,

01:24.117 --> 01:27.053
"I wish I could flip
the temple of my glasses

01:27.053 --> 01:29.222
and hold them in my hand."

01:29.222 --> 01:32.292
That was the moment that the
idea for Bunny Eyez was born.

01:32.292 --> 01:36.463
Bunny eyes are
the first wearable...

01:36.463 --> 01:38.865
tiltable...
flippable...

01:38.865 --> 01:40.400
O'Leary: Oh!
...reading glasses.

01:40.400 --> 01:42.202
Pretty cool, huh?
Wow.

01:42.202 --> 01:45.238
Bunny Eyez can be worn
or used comfortably

01:45.238 --> 01:47.073
no matter what activity
you're engaged in.

01:47.073 --> 01:49.609
Sitting on the couch,
you want to watch TV

01:49.609 --> 01:52.579
and scroll social media
at the same time?

01:52.579 --> 01:54.714
Just tilt the front
of your Bunny Eyez frame.

01:54.714 --> 01:56.216
You can do both.

01:56.216 --> 01:58.485
Lying on your side in bed
reading a book?

01:58.485 --> 01:59.986
Not a problem now.
Mnh-mnh.

01:59.986 --> 02:01.888
Just flip
one temple down.

02:01.888 --> 02:03.590
And boom -- you're
comfortable reading in bed.

02:03.590 --> 02:04.924
[ Laughter ]

02:04.924 --> 02:07.594
Sitting in the makeup chair
or at the salon,

02:07.594 --> 02:10.730
just hold your Bunny Eyez
like this.

02:10.730 --> 02:12.999
Bunny Eyez
even come in handy

02:12.999 --> 02:16.136
when you want to give
your teenager that look.

02:16.136 --> 02:18.004
You know the one.
[ Laughter ]

02:18.004 --> 02:21.074
We've taken the centuries-old
design of everyday glasses

02:21.074 --> 02:24.344
and made them so much more
functional and stylish.

02:24.344 --> 02:27.380
So, Sharks,
who's ready to wear...

02:27.380 --> 02:30.950
tilt, and flip their way
into a clearer future

02:30.950 --> 02:32.218
with Bunny Eyez?

02:32.218 --> 02:33.520
-Ah.
-Good job, good job.

02:33.520 --> 02:35.388
Sharks, in front of you
are samples of Bunny Eyez.

02:35.388 --> 02:36.789
-Yes.
-Thank you.

02:36.789 --> 02:39.159
