02:39.159 --> 02:42.595
So, I've got the arms down.
I get that.

02:42.595 --> 02:43.596
Jenny: Right. Yes.
And now I'm like this.

02:43.596 --> 02:45.064
Correct.
Okay.

02:45.064 --> 02:47.333
Jenny: So you all know,
it's a patented hinge.

02:47.333 --> 02:49.602
We have two utility patents.

02:49.602 --> 02:51.604
What's been
the response?

02:51.604 --> 02:53.940
We've had a really
tremendous response.

02:53.940 --> 02:55.875
