33:33.544 --> 33:34.579
[ Laughter ]

33:34.579 --> 33:35.913
So, Sharks, who's ready

33:35.913 --> 33:38.916
to elevate their
dessert game with...

33:38.916 --> 33:41.552
Both: Yum Crumbs?!
