34:20.358 --> 34:22.827
but it gets that
sprinkle consistency

34:22.827 --> 34:25.530
to be able to hold up
in just about any dessert.

34:25.530 --> 34:27.498
Are you selling this
for commercial use?

34:27.498 --> 34:29.634
Yes, that's
our biggest market. B2B.

